Steady pressure $BTC can last longer than you think. It causes people to add add add eventually panic selling on real flush forcing even lower. Not much support until $29.5-30k. After that you may get a serious crypto waterfall low to mid $20k's before fast bounce to high $20k's. https://t.co/S5JYLNNMcm https://t.co/6zzm4YQsBM

I would remind everyone trying to find "bottom" on $BTC could he a very long process. Too many body bags now. It can't just "pop" back up. It's a LONG process.

They have to clean up all "quick fix" players.

It took from Dec '17 until Nov '21 to break prior resistance levels. https://t.co/OghNth1RUb https://t.co/oZ24ys3KuY

As with any names - they need to go through cycles. Work out the folks looking to get rich off $BTC because their friend did.

One thing crypto has done is convince people to hold for something "later" just like $AMC

It's a supply and demand game.

Could take years. Just FYI. https://t.co/tpquFi2ayV
@TraderDan12 I still probably won't buy it.
November '20 **

I meant Nov '20 here not '21.

But point is 2 ... 3... 4 years to work through excess supply back into strong hands. 

At the end of the day it's like a small cap stock with tiny float. It works while supply is held and demand fears missing it - doesn't when supply exits. https://t.co/tpquFi2ayV

In my opinion be cautious getting in "it has to bounce" mode on $SPY

Sure, it will -- but they may be just short term relief bounces. We may have a HUGE rally but doesn't mean that's it.

The bottoming process in my opinion will be just like the topping - it'll take 2-3 months. https://t.co/zpetg9ovbq

I think this is important to consider because as you position it's no different than the short side. 

Think about what they had go through nearly 3 x market rolled and went back to highs. 

It's a process that has to play out. 

Let it play out - don't be played (ie: exhausted). https://t.co/ueKbykyJ9m

There will be a lot of indecision next few weeks/months.

Indecision means lots of bearish/panic moves turning bullish & bullish moves turning bearish/panic.

Be cautious getting BIASED.

There is a time to trade, time to invest. 

Don't MIX! If investing - don't try to trade it. https://t.co/hOzQW6DZ9a
